    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J1058">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Bloom -- is Result -- to meet a Flower</l>
                    <l>And casually glance</l>
                    <l>Would cause one scarcely to suspect</l>
                    <l>The minor Circumstance</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Assisting in the Bright Affair</l>
                    <l>So intricately done</l>
                    <l>Then offered as a Butterfly</l>
                    <l>To the Meridian --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>To pack the Bud -- oppose flu Worm --</l>
                    <l>Obtain it's right of Dew --</l>
                    <l>Adjust the Heat -- elude the Wind --</l>
                    <l>Escape the prowling Bee</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Great Nature not to disappoint</l>
                    <l>Awaiting Her that Day --</l>
                    <l>To be a Flower, is profound</l>
                    <l>Responsibility --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                </lg>

            </div>     
